item.title: OverTheWire.org Bandit Level 8 -> Level 9
item.description: http://overthewire.org/wargames/bandit/bandit9.html Bandit Level 8 → Level 9 Level Goal The password for the next level is stored in the file data.txt and is the only line of text that occurs only once Commands you may need to solve this level grep, sort, uniq, strings, base64, tr, tar, gzip, bzip2, xxd Helpful Reading Material The unix commandline: pipes and redirects Level 8에서 Level 9로 가기 위해서 data.txt 파일을 확인해봐야한다. 비밀번호는 단 한 문장만 존재한다고 한다.
